BACKSTORY:

Born beneath the crimson moon of Gearheaven, Lust is the final heir of an ancient vampire bloodline known for protecting the balance between monsters and mankind.

Unlike warriors who rely only on overwhelming strength, Lust believes every opponent has a weakness waiting to be discovered. Her curiosity became her greatest weapon as she studied combat patterns, learned enemy techniques, and mastered prediction.

Instead of using a traditional weapon, Lust transformed an enchanted giant lollipop into a legendary hunter weapon capable of piercing defenses, controlling battles, and overwhelming enemies with impossible speed.

After her vampire clan vanished during a forgotten conflict, Lust traveled across Gearheaven searching for the truth. During her journey, she uncovered ancient enchantments hidden within her weapon, unlocking the ability to bend attacks around defenses, move faster than sight, and strike before enemies can react.

Known as the Crimson Hunger, Lust is not feared because of destruction, but because of her endless desire to challenge powerful opponents and uncover hidden strength.

To enemies, she is an unpredictable vampire hunter who cannot be stopped.
To allies, she is a fearless warrior who always finds the perfect opening.

